Created class to create sets of edges for testing and for input - incomplete and untested at this time; algorithm doesn't pass tests right now - won't compile, due to need for better sets of input edge data for testing.
Created separate Edge class; wrote Edge unit tests; created new unit test file for ESB.

Added comments; added feature to choose directed/undirected graph; wrote additional unit tests for ShortestPath class.
